{
  "video_id": "RpgWy7S9wU8",
  "title": "PS. In Theory: Universal Basic Income",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 220.0,
      "end_time": 1900.0,
      "text": "The threat that technological innovation will"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 1900.0,
      "end_time": 4400.0,
      "text": "destroy more jobs than it creates has spurred"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4400.0,
      "end_time": 6940.0,
      "text": "a wide variety of proposals for ensuring that"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 6940.0,
      "end_time": 9260.0,
      "text": "workers aren’t left out in the cold."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 9270.0,
      "end_time": 12340.0,
      "text": "One such proposal is universal basic income."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 12340.0,
      "end_time": 14640.0,
      "text": "The idea is simple: citizens or permanent"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 14640.0,
      "end_time": 17160.0,
      "text": "residents receive a fixed sum of money, giving"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 17160.0,
      "end_time": 19600.0,
      "text": "them the security and flexibility to participate"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 19600.0,
      "end_time": 22900.0,
      "text": "in reskilling or higher education programs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 22900.0,
      "end_time": 24540.0,
      "text": "to start their own businesses, to engage in"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 24540.0,
      "end_time": 27340.0,
      "text": "less lucrative but socially valuable activities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 27340.0,
      "end_time": 29849.0,
      "text": "or simply to spend less time working."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 29849.0,
      "end_time": 31880.0,
      "text": "As the so-called gig economy grows, and unions’"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 31880.0,
      "end_time": 34920.0,
      "text": "capacity to protect workers weakens, a UBI"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 34920.0,
      "end_time": 37300.0,
      "text": "would be a powerful economic stabilizer."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 37300.0,
      "end_time": 39459.0,
      "text": "And, because it would be universal, a UBI"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 39460.0,
      "end_time": 41500.0,
      "text": "would lack the stigma or means-testing that"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 41500.0,
      "end_time": 43460.0,
      "text": "often weaken political support for existing"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 43460.0,
      "end_time": 45440.0,
      "text": "welfare programs."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 45440.0,
      "end_time": 48180.0,
      "text": "The most obvious question is how to pay for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 48180.0,
      "end_time": 50460.0,
      "text": "One option is taxation of corporate profits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 50460.0,
      "end_time": 52800.0,
      "text": "though any tax-based financing scheme would"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 52800.0,
      "end_time": 55180.0,
      "text": "almost certainly face powerful – and possibly"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 55180.0,
      "end_time": 57320.0,
      "text": "fatal – political resistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 57320.0,
      "end_time": 59760.0,
      "text": "Another option, advanced by Yanis Varoufakis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 59760.0,
      "end_time": 62000.0,
      "text": "seeks to avoid this problem by giving the"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 62000.0,
      "end_time": 64720.0,
      "text": "public a share of returns on capital."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 64720.0,
      "end_time": 67800.0,
      "text": "For example, a percentage of capital stock"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 67800.0,
      "end_time": 68970.0,
      "text": "(shares) from every initial public offering"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 68970.0,
      "end_time": 70980.0,
      "text": "could be channeled into a Commons Capital"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 70980.0,
      "end_time": 73120.0,
      "text": "Depository, with the dividends funding what"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 73120.0,
      "end_time": 76320.0,
      "text": "would amount to a universal income scheme."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 76330.0,
      "end_time": 78950.0,
      "text": "But financing UBI is just the first step."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 78950.0,
      "end_time": 81160.0,
      "text": "The concept challenges traditional ideas about"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 81160.0,
      "end_time": 83700.0,
      "text": "work, success, and human fulfillment."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 83700.0,
      "end_time": 85580.0,
      "text": "On the right, critics worry that a UBI would"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 85580.0,
      "end_time": 87649.0,
      "text": "give rise to mass dependency, with a large"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 87650.0,
      "end_time": 89540.0,
      "text": "share of the population no longer bothering"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 89540.0,
      "end_time": 91900.0,
      "text": "to work, leading to a drop in labor supply"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 91900.0,
      "end_time": 94140.0,
      "text": "and falling productivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 94140.0,
      "end_time": 95880.0,
      "text": "Critics on the left, meanwhile, worry that"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 95880.0,
      "end_time": 98000.0,
      "text": "the UBI could be used as a Trojan horse for"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 98000.0,
      "end_time": 99940.0,
      "text": "cutting other social programs that are meant"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 99940.0,
      "end_time": 102460.0,
      "text": "to target disadvantaged groups."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 102460.0,
      "end_time": 105720.0,
      "text": "In any case, UBI is not the only potential solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 105720.0,
      "end_time": 108600.0,
      "text": "For example, in the United States, some advocate"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 108600.0,
      "end_time": 110590.0,
      "text": "the expansion of the earned income tax credit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 110590.0,
      "end_time": 112520.0,
      "text": "which benefits low-income workers based on"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 112520.0,
      "end_time": 114440.0,
      "text": "how many hours they work and children they"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 114440.0,
      "end_time": 115440.0,
      "text": "have."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 115450.0,
      "end_time": 118270.0,
      "text": "Some also advocate a guaranteed jobs program."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 118270.0,
      "end_time": 120140.0,
      "text": "The federal government would guarantee employment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 120140.0,
      "end_time": 122400.0,
      "text": "with benefits and a living wage, to every"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 122400.0,
      "end_time": 124120.0,
      "text": "citizen or permanent resident willing and"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 124120.0,
      "end_time": 125500.0,
      "text": "able to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 125500.0,
      "end_time": 127460.0,
      "text": "Among other things, a job guarantee, like"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 127460.0,
      "end_time": 129859.0,
      "text": "a UBI, would boost workers’ negotiating"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 129860.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131880.0,
      "text": "power throughout the economy by removing the"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 131880.0,
      "end_time": 134120.0,
      "text": "fear of unemployment."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 134120.0,
      "end_time": 136100.0,
      "text": "None of these proposals has yet been implemented,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 136100.0,
      "end_time": 138400.0,
      "text": "at least not on a scale large enough to assess"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 138400.0,
      "end_time": 139400.0,
      "text": "them properly."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 139400.0,
      "end_time": 141660.0,
      "text": "And, for now, the political will to test bold"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 141660.0,
      "end_time": 144000.0,
      "text": "solutions is lacking in much of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 144000.0,
      "end_time": 146380.0,
      "text": "But with the specter of technological unemployment"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 146380.0,
      "end_time": 149000.0,
      "text": "closing in, governments may soon have no choice"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 149000.0,
      "end_time": 151000.0,
      "text": "but to test novel ideas."
    }
  ]
}